sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Dashboard
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Proxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant API as DSP API Server<br/>8888/TCP HTTPS
    participant DB as MariaDB<br/>3306/TCP MySQL
    participant S3 as S3 Object Store<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant K8s as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Argo as Argo Workflow Controller
    participant Task as Pipeline Task Pod
    participant MLMD as MLMD gRPC Server<br/>8080/TCP gRPC
    participant PA as Persistence Agent

    Note over User,S3: Flow 1: Pipeline Submission
    User->>Route: POST /apis/v2beta1/*<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    Route->>Proxy: Forward (TLS reencrypt)
    Proxy->>K8s: SubjectAccessReview<br/>DSPA api subresource
    K8s-->>Proxy: Allowed
    Proxy->>API: Forward request<br/>TLS (pod-to-pod)
    API->>DB: Store pipeline metadata<br/>TLS, username/password
    API->>S3: Store pipeline artifacts<br/>TLS, AccessKey/SecretKey
    API-->>Route: Pipeline created
    Route-->>User: JSON Response

    Note over API,Task: Flow 2: Pipeline Execution
    API->>K8s: Create Workflow CR<br/>ServiceAccount token
    K8s-->>Argo: Workflow event
    Argo->>K8s: Create task pods<br/>ServiceAccount token
    K8s-->>Task: Pod scheduled
    Task->>API: Report status<br/>8888/TCP, TLS, SA token
    Task->>S3: Upload artifacts<br/>443/TCP, TLS, AccessKey
    Task->>MLMD: Store metadata<br/>8080/TCP, gRPC, TLS

    Note over PA,API: Flow 3: Persistence Agent Sync
    PA->>API: Sync run status<br/>8888/TCP, TLS (pod-to-pod)
    PA->>K8s: Watch Workflow CRs<br/>6443/TCP, TLS, SA token

    Note over User,K8s: Flow 4: Operator Reconciliation
    participant DSPO as DSPO Controller
    DSPO->>K8s: Watch DSPA CRs<br/>6443/TCP, TLS, SA token
    DSPO->>DB: Health check<br/>3306/TCP, TLS
    DSPO->>S3: Health check<br/>443/TCP, TLS
    DSPO->>K8s: Deploy components<br/>via manifestival templates
